#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:2
msgid "Maximize Your Microsoft Investments"
msgstr "Microsoft 투자 극대화"

#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:4
msgid ""
"Unlock the full potential of your Microsoft Teams, M365, and Entra ID "
"investment with Mattermost. Designed for operational teams that require "
"advanced customization, secure workflows, and seamless deployment on "
"segregated networks, Mattermost enhances your existing Microsoft "
"solutions for critical mission success."
msgstr ""
"Mattermost를 통해 Microsoft Teams, M365, Entra ID 투자의 전체 잠재력을 발휘하세요. 고급 사용자 정의, "
"보안 워크플로우, 분리된 네트워크에서의 원활한 배포가 필요한 운영 팀을 위해 설계된 Mattermost는 중요한 "
"미션 성공을 위해 기존 Microsoft 솔루션을 강화합니다."

#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:6
msgid ""
"Mattermost complements Microsoft solutions with tailored capabilities "
"designed to meet the unique needs of high-security environments, inter-"
"agency collaboration, and external workflows, enabling teams to maximize "
"their Microsoft investment."
msgstr ""
"Mattermost는 고보안 환경, 기관 간 협업, 외부 워크플로우의 고유한 요구사항을 충족하도록 설계된 맞춤형 기능으로 "
"Microsoft 솔루션을 보완하여 팀이 Microsoft 투자를 극대화할 수 있도록 합니다."

#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:8
msgid "The following mission-ready collaboration capabilities are available:"
msgstr "다음과 같은 미션 준비된 협업 기능을 사용할 수 있습니다:"

#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:11
msgid "On-Premises Skype for Business Replacement"
msgstr "온프레미스 Skype for Business 대체"

#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:13
msgid ""
"As Skype for Business reaches end-of-life, secure organizations require "
"an alternative that preserves on-premises control, integrates into "
"Microsoft workflows, and meets the security standards of air-gapped and "
"classified environments. Cloud-first replacements like Microsoft Teams "
"are not always viable due to network segmentation, compliance "
"restrictions, or data sovereignty mandates."
msgstr ""
"Skype for Business가 수명 종료에 도달함에 따라, 보안 조직은 온프레미스 제어를 유지하고 Microsoft "
"워크플로우에 통합되며 에어갭 및 분류된 환경의 보안 표준을 충족하는 대안이 필요합니다. Microsoft Teams와 같은 "
"클라우드 우선 대체 솔루션은 네트워크 분할, 규정 준수 제한 또는 데이터 주권 요구사항으로 인해 항상 실행 가능하지는 "
"않습니다."

#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:15
msgid ""
"**Preserve mission-critical communication workflows** with a self-hosted "
"Mattermost deployment that supports :doc:`1:1 calls </collaborate/make-"
"calls>`, :ref:`screen sharing <collaborate/make-calls:share your "
"screen>`, and :doc:`threaded messaging </collaborate/organize-"
"conversations>` within secure environments."
msgstr ""
"보안 환경 내에서 :doc:`1:1 통화 </collaborate/make-calls>`, :ref:`화면 공유 "
"<collaborate/make-calls:share your screen>`, :doc:`스레드 메시징 </collaborate/organize-"
"conversations>` 을 지원하는 자체 호스팅 Mattermost 배포로 **미션 크리티컬 통신 워크플로우를 "
"유지** 하세요."

#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:16
msgid ""
"**Integrate Mattermost with Microsoft tools** such as Outlook, Teams, and"
" :doc:`Entra ID Single Sign-On </onboard/sso-entraid>` to retain user "
"workflows while centralizing identity and access control. See "
":doc:`Mattermost for M365, Teams, and Outlook </integrate/mattermost-"
"mission-collaboration-for-m365>`."
msgstr ""
"Outlook, Teams, :doc:`Entra ID Single Sign-On </onboard/sso-entraid>` 와 같은 Microsoft 도구와 "
"Mattermost를 통합하여 ID 및 액세스 제어를 중앙화하면서 사용자 워크플로우를 유지하세요. "
":doc:`M365, Teams, Outlook용 Mattermost </integrate/mattermost-mission-collaboration-for-m365>` 를 "
"참조하세요."

#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:17
msgid ""
"**Deploy in sovereign, air-gapped, or private cloud environments** such "
"as `Azure Deployment <https://azuremarketplace.microsoft.com/en-"
"us/marketplace/apps/mattermost.mattermost-operator?tab=overview>`_ while "
"maintaining compliance with STIG, FedRAMP, and NIST 800-53 standards."
msgstr ""
"`Azure Deployment <https://azuremarketplace.microsoft.com/en-us/marketplace/apps/mattermost.mattermost-"
"operator?tab=overview>`_ 와 같은 주권, 에어갭 또는 프라이빗 클라우드 환경에 배포하면서 STIG, FedRAMP, "
"NIST 800-53 표준을 준수하세요."

#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:19
msgid ""
":doc:`Learn more </about/on-prem-skype-for-business-replacement>` about "
"replacing Skype for Business with Mattermost."
msgstr ""
"Mattermost로 Skype for Business를 대체하는 방법에 대해 :doc:`자세히 알아보세요 "
"</about/on-prem-skype-for-business-replacement>`."

#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:22
msgid "Out-of-Band Incident Response for Microsoft-Centric Environments"
msgstr "Microsoft 중심 환경을 위한 대역 외 인시던트 대응"

#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:24
msgid ""
"During high-stakes incidents, Microsoft 365 tools can be limited or "
"unavailable, slowing down response times and jeopardizing mission "
"continuity."
msgstr ""
"위험도가 높은 인시던트 발생 시 Microsoft 365 도구가 제한되거나 사용할 수 없어 대응 시간이 지연되고 "
"미션 연속성이 위협받을 수 있습니다."

#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:26
#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:38
#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:50
#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:62
msgid "**Benefits**"
msgstr "**이점**"

#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:28
msgid ""
"**Maintain operational continuity during M365 outages** with a dedicated,"
" out-of-band Mattermost instance for secure incident response, "
"communication, and collaboration. See :doc:`Playbooks in Microsoft Teams "
"</integrate/playbooks-for-microsoft-teams>`"
msgstr ""
"**M365 중단 중에도 운영 연속성 유지** - 안전한 인시던트 대응, 통신 및 협업을 위한 전용 대역 외 Mattermost 인스턴스를 통해 "
"가능합니다. :doc:`Microsoft Teams의 Playbooks </integrate/playbooks-for-microsoft-teams>` 를 참조하세요."

#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:29
msgid ""
"**Accelerate responses** with :ref:`AI-powered workflows <configure"
"/enable-copilot:mattermost configuration>`, enabling structured playbooks"
" for triage, escalation, and resolution even when primary systems are "
"compromised."
msgstr ""
"**AI 기반 워크플로우를 통해 대응 속도 향상** - :ref:`Mattermost 설정에서 Copilot 기능 활성화 <configure/enable-copilot:mattermost configuration>` 로 "
"분류, 에스컬레이션, 해결을 위한 구조화된 플레이북을 주요 시스템이 손상된 상황에서도 사용할 수 있습니다."

#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:30
msgid ""
"**Integrate with Microsoft Security Suite** and :doc:`Entra ID </onboard"
"/sso-entraid>` to preserve centralized identity management while keeping "
"sensitive data in a secure secondary system. :doc:`Learn more "
"</about/integrations>` about Mattermost's integration capabilities."
msgstr ""
"**Microsoft Security Suite와 통합하고**, :doc:`Entra ID </onboard/sso-entraid>` 를 통해 중앙화된 ID 관리를 유지하면서 "
"민감한 데이터를 안전한 보조 시스템에 보관할 수 있습니다. Mattermost의 통합 기능에 대해 :doc:`자세히 알아보세요 </about/integrations>`."

#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:31
msgid ""
"**Protect breach-sensitive notifications** using :ref:`ID-only push "
"alerts <configure/environment-configuration-settings:id-only push "
"notifications>` and enhanced mobile security, enabling secure "
"communication without cloud exposure."
msgstr ""
":ref:`ID 전용 푸시 알림 <configure/environment-configuration-settings:id-only push notifications>` 과 "
"향상된 모바일 보안을 사용하여 위반에 민감한 알림을 보호합니다. 이 기능은 클라우드에 노출되지 않고도 안전한 통신을 가능하게 합니다."

#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:34
msgid "External Collaboration with Full Control"
msgstr "완전한 제어가 가능한 외부 협업"

#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:36
msgid ""
"Managing external collaboration within Microsoft Teams can be complex, "
"often requiring numerous configurations and administration that lead to "
"security risks like usage of consumer-grade chat tools."
msgstr ""
"Microsoft Teams 내에서 외부 협업을 관리하는 것은 복잡할 수 있으며, 종종 소비자용 채팅 도구 사용과 같은 보안 위험을 초래하는 "
"다수의 구성 및 관리가 필요합니다."

#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:40
msgid ""
"**Integrate Mattermost with Microsoft Teams and Outlook** to enable "
"secure external collaboration with encryption, audit trails, and role-"
"based permissions—without compromising compliance. (See :doc:`Mattermost "
"for M365, Teams, and Outlook </integrate/mattermost-mission-"
"collaboration-for-m365>`)."
msgstr ""
"**Mattermost를 Microsoft Teams 및 Outlook과 통합** 하여 암호화, 감사 추적 및 역할 기반 권한을 갖춘 안전한 외부 협업을 "
"활성화하세요 - 규정 준수를 저해하지 않으면서. (:doc:`M365, Teams, Outlook용 Mattermost "
"</integrate/mattermost-mission-collaboration-for-m365>` 참조)."

#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:41
msgid ""
"**Eliminate shadow IT** by providing :doc:`Connected Workspaces </onboard"
"/connected-workspaces>` for sanctioned, policy-enforced engagement with "
"external partners—reducing reliance on consumer-grade tools."
msgstr ""
"**섀도우 IT 제거** - :doc:`Connected Workspaces </onboard/connected-workspaces>` 를 통해 "
"외부 파트너와의 정책 기반 참여를 제공하여 소비자용 도구에 대한 의존성을 줄입니다."

#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:42
msgid ""
"**Apply granular policy enforcement for external users**, including "
":ref:`granular user permissions <manage/team-channel-members:advanced "
"access controls>`, :doc:`legal hold </comply/legal-hold>`, "
":doc:`retention policies </comply/data-retention-policy>`, and "
":doc:`custom Terms of Service </comply/custom-terms-of-service>`."
msgstr ""
"**외부 사용자를 위한 세분화된 정책 적용** - :ref:`세분화된 사용자 권한 <manage/team-channel-members:advanced access controls>`, "
":doc:`법적 보관 </comply/legal-hold>`, :doc:`보존 정책 </comply/data-retention-policy>`, "
"그리고 :doc:`사용자 정의 서비스 약관 </comply/custom-terms-of-service>` 을 포함합니다."

#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:43
msgid ""
"**Synchronize user identity** using :doc:`Entra ID </onboard/sso-"
"entraid>` to maintain scalable, centralized access control across both "
"internal and external collaborators."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Entra ID </onboard/sso-entraid>` 를 사용하여 **사용자 ID 동기화** - 내부 및 외부 협업자 간에 "
"확장 가능한 중앙화된 액세스 제어를 유지합니다."

#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:46
msgid "Sovereign Communication in Microsoft Teams"
msgstr "Microsoft Teams의 주권적 통신"

#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:48
msgid ""
"Agencies and critical infrastructure organizations must often comply with"
" strict data sovereignty rules that restrict cloud usage for sensitive "
"collaboration."
msgstr ""
"기관과 중요 인프라 조직은 종종 민감한 협업을 위한 클라우드 사용을 제한하는 엄격한 데이터 주권 규칙을 준수해야 합니다."

#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:52
msgid ""
"**Deploy Mattermost on-premise or in sovereign clouds**, fully integrated"
" with Microsoft Teams and Outlook (See :doc:`Mattermost for M365, Teams, "
"and Outlook </integrate/mattermost-mission-collaboration-for-m365>`) to "
"maintain workflow continuity and secure data storage."
msgstr ""
"**Mattermost를 온프레미스 또는 주권 클라우드에 배포** - Microsoft Teams 및 Outlook과 완전히 통합되어 "
"(:doc:`M365, Teams, Outlook용 Mattermost </integrate/mattermost-mission-collaboration-for-m365>` 참조) "
"워크플로우 연속성과 안전한 데이터 저장을 유지합니다."

#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:53
msgid ""
"**Store messages, recordings, and transcriptions in compliance-approved "
"systems**, with :ref:`data-at-rest encryption <about/security:data-at-"
"rest encryption>` ensuring no leakage of sensitive data to third-party "
"platforms."
msgstr ""
"**메시지, 녹음 및 전사를 규정 준수 승인 시스템에 저장** - :ref:`휴지 데이터 암호화 <about/security:data-at-rest encryption>` 를 통해 "
"민감한 데이터가 서드파티 플랫폼으로 유출되지 않도록 보장합니다."

#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:54
msgid ""
"**Enable secure Microsoft Teams interactions via embedded Mattermost "
"collaboration**, supporting operations within familiar interfaces while "
"enforcing regulatory compliance. See :doc:`Mattermost for M365, Teams, "
"and Outlook </integrate/mattermost-mission-collaboration-for-m365>`."
msgstr ""
"**내장된 Mattermost 협업을 통해 안전한 Microsoft Teams 상호작용 활성화** - 규제 준수를 강제하면서도 "
"친숙한 인터페이스 내에서 운영을 지원합니다. :doc:`M365, Teams, Outlook용 Mattermost "
"</integrate/mattermost-mission-collaboration-for-m365>` 를 참조하세요."

#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:55
msgid ""
"**Enforce agency-specific policies** with :doc:`legal hold </comply"
"/legal-hold>`, :doc:`retention policies </comply/data-retention-policy>`,"
" and :doc:`user access controls </onboard/advanced-permissions>` that "
"align with national or sectoral mandates."
msgstr ""
"국가 또는 부문별 지침에 맞춰 :doc:`법적 보관 </comply/legal-hold>`, :doc:`보존 정책 "
"</comply/data-retention-policy>`, :doc:`사용자 액세스 제어 </onboard/advanced-permissions>` 를 통해 "
"**기관별 정책을 적용** 합니다."

#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:58
msgid "Cross-Instance Collaboration Hub"
msgstr "크로스 인스턴스 협업 허브"

#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:60
msgid ""
"Multi-agency, multi-tenant Microsoft 365 environments often hinder "
"seamless collaboration and increase complexity for inter-organization "
"workflows."
msgstr ""
"다중 기관, 다중 테넌트 Microsoft 365 환경은 종종 원활한 협업을 방해하고 조직 간 워크플로우의 복잡성을 "
"증가시킵니다."

#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:64
msgid ""
"**Centralize communication across M365 instances** using Mattermost as a "
"neutral, embedded hub for messaging, file sharing, and playbook "
"coordination (See :doc:`Mattermost for M365, Teams, and Outlook "
"</integrate/mattermost-mission-collaboration-for-m365>`)."
msgstr ""
"Mattermost를 메시징, 파일 공유, 플레이북 조정을 위한 중립적이고 내장된 허브로 사용하여 **M365 인스턴스 간 "
"통신을 중앙화** 합니다 (:doc:`M365, Teams, Outlook용 Mattermost "
"</integrate/mattermost-mission-collaboration-for-m365>` 참조)."

#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:65
msgid ""
"**Bridge segmented Teams deployments** with :doc:`Connected Workspaces "
"</onboard/connected-workspaces>` and Microsoft presence integration to "
"ensure continuity without duplicative configuration."
msgstr ""
":doc:`연결된 작업 공간 </onboard/connected-workspaces>` 및 Microsoft 상태 통합을 통해 **분할된 "
"Teams 배포를 연결** 하여 중복 구성 없이 연속성을 보장합니다."

#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:66
msgid ""
"**Deploy flexibly across hybrid, private, or air-gapped environments** "
"such as :doc:`Mattermost for M365, Teams, and Outlook </integrate"
"/mattermost-mission-collaboration-for-m365>` to ensure operational "
"consistency no matter the deployment complexity."
msgstr ""
":doc:`M365, Teams, Outlook용 Mattermost </integrate/mattermost-mission-collaboration-for-m365>` 와 "
"같은 하이브리드, 프라이빗 또는 에어갭 환경에 **유연하게 배포** 하여 배포 복잡성에 관계없이 운영 일관성을 "
"보장합니다."

#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:67
msgid ""
"**Secure external communications and maintain control** with "
"segmentation, data governance, and compliance automation across Teams "
"ecosystems."
msgstr ""
"Teams 생태계 전반에 걸쳐 세분화, 데이터 거버넌스 및 규정 준수 자동화를 통해 **외부 통신을 보안하고 "
"제어를 유지** 합니다."

#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:70
msgid "Get Started"
msgstr "시작하기"

#: ../../source/about/maximize-microsoft-investments.rst:72
msgid ""
"`Try Mattermost <https://mattermost.com/download/>`__ or `talk to an "
"Expert <https://mattermost.com/contact/>`__ to discover how your "
"organization can enhance Microsoft-based workflows with secure, "
"extensible collaboration tailored for operational and compliance-"
"sensitive environments. Maximize your Microsoft investment while "
"extending its capabilities into the most demanding mission contexts."
msgstr ""
"`Mattermost 사용해보기 <https://mattermost.com/download/>`__ 또는 `전문가와 상담하기 "
"<https://mattermost.com/contact/>`__ 를 통해 귀사의 조직이 운영 및 규정 준수에 민감한 환경에 맞춤화된 "
"안전하고 확장 가능한 협업으로 Microsoft 기반 워크플로우를 향상시킬 수 있는 방법을 알아보세요. 가장 까다로운 "
"미션 컨텍스트로 기능을 확장하면서 Microsoft 투자를 극대화하세요."

